Package org.eclipse.cdt.utils.macho

Class MachOHelper64

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.cdt.utils.macho.MachOHelper64
public class MachOHelper64 extends Object
MachOHelper64 is a wrapper class for the MachO64 class to provide higher level API for sorting/searching the MachO data.
Since:
5.2
